thread.title: Micronas announces global distribution agreement with Mouser Electronics
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Micronas announces global distribution agreement with Mouser Electronics | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Micronas announces global distribution agreement with Mouser Electronics
text:
Sept 24 Micronas Semiconductor Holding AG :
* Announces global distribution agreement with Mouser Electronics
* With this new contract, Mouser will distribute hall-effect sensors and embedded motor controllers from Micronas to customers around the globe Source text - bit.ly/1YCNXqN (Gdynia Newsroom)
